headline.main: Fan-Friendly Event Kicks Off Iditarod Race Across Alaska
headline.print_headline: Fan-Friendly Event Kicks Off Iditarod Race Across Alaska

lead_paragraph: Manchester United striker Zlatan Ibrahimovic said Bournemouth defender Tyrone Mings "jumped into my elbow" after the two came together in a challenge during the Premier League match at Old Trafford on Saturday.
